{"tid":1514923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有有份參與遊行示威既人士","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:17:59.000Z","uid":53419,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf1b041c0d3301c18226d4cbc01433b1ee3159a","tid":1514923,"uid":53419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由六月開始堅持到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，由69一百萬人去到二百萬人都冇放棄過！<br />\n即使發夢時大家三唔識七，都可以好似好有默契既隊友咁。即使中間發生過唔少爭執，仍然可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不篤灰、不抹黑、不分化、不割蓆</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n都係多得香港人既團結 可能呢個就係香港人既特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外所有好鼓舞既不合作運動，手拖手，和你飛，十點鳩叫活動，相信只有呢班咁可愛既香港人先會諗到，令大家可以堅持落去，對抗極權政府同惡法。直到今日，和理非、文宣組、支援組、勇武前線仔，全部都仲堅持緊！！<br />\n<br />\n見到手足放棄生命，一個個被補同埋受傷既義士，真係好撚傷心好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然香港人並唔希望有更多呢種情況出現，但係呢場戰爭係要繼續落去架！<br />\n你要知道，就算你行得攰，行得辛苦，仲有好多同路人陪你行落去！<br />\n行得攰咪最多去休息下去hea下做下港豬，仲有好多巴打接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千祈唔好放棄呀！仲未完架！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nStdmgk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnStdmgk.gif&h=99b134f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=0fabac65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=66abf9c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=91ab140c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"14690e4b1b732b1afa3321f2c495985668ea774e","tid":1514923,"uid":35842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=0fabac65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?